data.description: Welcome home to this inviting two story END unit Townhome in Arbor Oaks situated on a beautiful pond lot! As soon as you walk through the door you will be invited by the tall ceilings of the foyer, that lead you to the open floor plan between the living room and kitchen! The Kitchen features white cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances with both electric & gas options! This rare town-home features Dual masters, one being conveniently located downstairs over looking the pond lot. Just off the back door is the patio with a storage closet and your very own entrance to Summerville's Surreal Sawmill Trail! Head upstairs and stop to notice the newly finished oak-wood stair treads. All the bedrooms are spacious and just about every bedroom has their own bathroom in this home!Conveniently located to the charming town of Summerville with all of the shopping you can ask for!  SAVE SAVE SAVE your money because this low maintenance town-home has a NEW AC unit & New Hot water heater!  ...but wait there's more! The downstairs bathroom has a SECRET space, if you slide the mirror to the right that can be used for that EXTRA storage space!  Come see this home today!
